CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 26, 1955, pg. A1 reads: "Pyramids - New members of the Delta Sigma Theta Sorority's pledge club, the Pyramid, at the U. of Pittsburgh, are Dorothy Pridgen and Carrie Warley. They were feted at the home of Soror Susie Boone. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of seven women, including Delta Sigma Theta sorority pledges Carrie Warley seated on left with Dorothy Pridgen wearing a light colored sleeveless dress with dot pattern on scoop neck collar, posed in living room of Susie Boone with zigzag patterned sofa and geometrically patterned curtains
